bug.short_desc: review Gerrit for Connector discovery listing

long_desc.thetext:
I would like to add the Gerrit connector to the discovery listing.
Given the potential for listing other connectors such as review board I would suggest that we create a new category for "Code Review Management".
The UI review has been completed. The Gerrit connector will be included in the discovery listing with the Mylyn 3.7 release (bug 343617).
